  "texts": [
    "To improve the network's generalizability and reduce overfitting, data augmentation is heavily used in deep neural network training nowadays.",
    "There are currently no data augmentation operations that can cover all variations of the data, as they are all manually designed operations, such as rotation and color jittering.",
    "The search space of Cubuk et al.",
    "(261) was still restricted to basic handcrafted image processing operations when they proposed to learn an augmentation policy with reinforcement learning.",
    "As a result, GANs are much more flexible for augmenting the training data, as they can sample the whole distribution of data (262)."
